    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45732,45976,46220,46552,46732</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45872,46644</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Albert</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ね、&lt;Dio&gt;……ダオス戦役のことが
書いてある本ってある？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, &lt;Dio&gt;... Do you have the book Dhaos' History is written to?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あるけど……全部、家だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have it but...it's all the way back home.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;～、おらの中に『ダオス戦役のひみつ』、
『こども歴史大百科』があっただよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! I have inside of me "The Secrets of Dhaos' History" and "The Boy's Historical Journey"!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45980</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……それ、オレの本！
何、勝手に持ってきてんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>H-hey! That's my book! You and your convenient tricks!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46056</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがと、アルベルトさん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you Mister Albert!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ふんふん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、どーしたんだよ、
今まで興味なかったくせに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why the sudden urge anyways?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>みんなのしてる話が全然、わかんないから、
このままじゃいけないと思ったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't understand everything everyone talks about, I can't keep up like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こういうことは、ちゃんと知っておかないと
ダメなんだよ、きっと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll try not to end up in this position again, I promise!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>相変わらず&lt;Mel&gt;って真面目だよな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Usual &lt;Mel&gt;, I see...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ～、どこぞのチビ助と違って、な！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see this is usual brat idiocy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_021_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うるせー！　本棚に作り変えちまうぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh shut up! You are the one that stole the books in the first place!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
